        "installation": "<p>To install:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Drop the &#8216;social-counter-widget&#8217; folder into your &#8216;wp-content/plugins&#8217; folder</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Go to your Administration: Plugins page and activate the &#8220;Social Counter Widget&#8221;</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>To configure:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to Appearance: Widgets </li>\n<li>Move (drag and drop) the widget to your desired location in the active sidebar. </li>\n<li>Enter Full Facebook URL, Twitter ID and Full Feedburner URL and save changes.</li>\n</ol>\n",
